{"url": "http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2016/06/14/an-open-letter-to-omar-mateen-from-a-survivor-of-the-orlando-nightclub-shooting_n_10453824.html", "date": "2016-06-14", "content": "I'm a young, gay man who was born in New Jersey and grew up in Orlando. I love my friends, I love my parents, I\u2019m half Puerto Rican, half Dominican, 21 years old, and at 2 a.m. on Sunday morning, you almost took my life.\nI go to Pulse nightclub in Orlando because I feel comfortable there, and I can be myself. Several of my friends were there that night, including my friend Stanley. I will never see Stanley again. You took that away from me.\u00a0", "title": "An Open Letter To Omar Mateen From A Survivor Of The Orlando Nightclub Shooting"}